HEADWORD: Unpervert
<hw>Un`per*vert</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>pervert</ets>.]</ety> <def>To free from
perversion; to deliver from being perverted; to reconvert.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
